How To Install
==============

1.	Copy the files from this repository into your theme directory

2.	Add the following to your functions.php file:

		require_once get_stylesheet_directory() . '/inc/recaptchalib.php';
		require_once get_stylesheet_directory() . '/inc/custom-login-register.php';
		$custom_login_register = new yourapp\Registration;

3.	Sign up for a reCAPTCHA account here:  https://www.google.com/recaptcha/

4.	Update the reCAPTCHA credentials in the top of inc/custom-login-register.php with your reCAPTCHA credentials

5.	Create a page called "Register" and a page called "Login" (these need to be setup at /register and /login permalinks)